snippet.title: FIRST KISS AT A SPOOKY SOIREE - Romantic Visual Novel
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://nomnomnami.itch.io/first-kiss-at-a-spooky-soiree?ac=qfCyYFQF A visual novel created for Yuri Jam 2016. you play as marzipan, a light witch who's gone her whole life without kissing anyone--UNTIL TONIGHT! there are 10 endings, with 8 characters to kiss.
